'''Theunis Willem de Jongh''' was the fifth Governor of the [[South African Reserve Bank]].<ref>{{cite news|url=https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=wHkzAAAAIBAJ&sjid=5-oFAAAAIBAJ&pg=4983,4098103&dq=theunis-willem-de-jongh&hl=en|title=South African Bank Rate Cut|date=10 August 1972|work=[[Miami News]]|accessdate=25 October 2010}}</ref> His term of office was from 1 July 1967 to 31 December 1980.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.reservebank.co.za/internet/publication.nsf/WCEV/3EE37129EFC921CD42256F630041551E/?opendocument|title=Theunis Willem de Jongh - Profile|publisher=[[South African Reserve Bank]]|accessdate=25 October 2010}}</ref> He was succeeded by [[Gerhard de Kock]].
